Post.title: Git
Post.author: Pyker
Post._content:
gitgit[Git](https://git-scm.com/docs)
```bash
git init                                                  # git
git config --global user.name "xxx"                       # 
git config --global user.email "xxx@xxx.com"              # 
git config --global color.ui true                         # git status
git config --global color.status auto
git config --global color.diff auto
git config --global color.branch auto
git config --global color.interactive auto
git clone git+ssh://git@192.168.53.168/VT.git             # clone
git status                                                # 
git add xyz                                               # xyz
git add .                                                 # 
git commit -m 'xxx'                                       # 
git commit --amend -m 'xxx'                               # 
git commit -am 'xxx'                                      # addcommit
git rm xxx                                                # 
git rm -r *                                               # 
git log                                                   # 
git log -1                                                # 1commit -nn
git log -5 --oneline									  # 5commit
git log --stat                                            # 
git log --graph --pretty=oneline --abbrev-commit          # 
git show dfb02e6e4f2f7b573337763e5c0013802e392818         # 
git show dfb02                                            # commitid
git show HEAD                                             # HEAD
git show HEAD^                                            # HEAD
git show HEAD~10                                          # 10
git show -s --pretty=raw 2be7fcb476
git tag                                                   # tag
git tag -a v2.0 -m 'xxx'                                  # v2.0tag
git show v2.0                                             # v2.0
git log v2.0                                              # v2.0
git diff                                                  # 
git diff --cached                                         # indexcommit
git diff HEAD^                                            # 
git diff HEAD -- ./lib                                    # HEADlib
git diff origin/master..master                            # mastermaster
git diff origin/master..master --stat                     # 
git remote add origin git+ssh://git@192.168.53.168/VT.git # push/pull/fetch
git branch                                                # 
git branch --contains 50089                               # 50089
git branch -a                                             # 
git branch -r                                             # 
git branch --merged                                       # 
git branch --no-merged                                    # 
git branch -m master master_copy                          # 
git checkout -b master_copy                               # master_copy
git checkout -b dev origin/dev                            # devdev
git checkout features/performance                         # features/performance
git checkout --track hotfix/BJP93                         # hotfix/BJP93
git checkout v2.0                                         # v2.0
git checkout -b devel origin/develop                      # developdevel
git checkout -- README                                    # README()
git merge --no-ff origin/master                           # master
git cherry-pick ff44785404a8e                             # ff44785404a8e
git push origin master                                    # masterpushmaster
git push origin :hotfixes/BJVEP933                        # hotfixes/BJVEP933
git push --tags                                           # tag
git push --set-upstream origin dev                        # dev
git fetch                                                 # merge
git fetch --prune                                         # 
git fetch origin dev:tmp                                  # devtmp
git pull origin master                                    # mastermerge
git mv README README2                                     # READMEREADME2
git reset --hard 2f3c                                     # 2f3cmerge
git rebase
git branch -d hotfix                                      # hotfix ()
git branch -D hotfix/BJP93                                # hotfix/BJP93
git ls-files                                              # git 
git show-branch                                           # 
git show-branch --all                                     # 
git whatchanged                                           # 
git revert dfb02e6e4                                      # dfb02e6e4
git ls-tree HEAD                                          # git
git rev-parse v2.0                                        # refSHA1 HASH
git reflog                                                # 
git show HEAD@{5}
git show master@{yesterday}                               # master
git log --pretty=format:'%h %s' --graph                   # 
git stash                                                 # HEAD
git stash list                                            # 
git stash show -p stash@{0}                               # 
git stash apply stash@{0}                                 # 
git stash drop                                            # stash
git stash pop                                             #  git stash applygit stash drop
git grep "delete from"                                    # delete from
git grep -e '#define' --and -e SORT_DIRENT
git gc
git fsck
```
### git fetch git pull 
* git fetch merge
```bash
git fetch                                 # branch
git diff origin/master                    # masterorigin/master
git diff HEAD FETCH_HEAD                  # 
git merge origin/master                   # 
```

```bash
git fetch origin master:tmp        # mastertmp
git diff tmp                       # tmp
git merge tmp                      # tmp
```
* git pullmerge
```bash
git pull origin master
```
git pull merge
git fetch
